<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Plan Nutricional - Sergio Gómez</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bebas+Neue&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --bg: #0f0f0f;
    --card: #181818;
    --card2: #1f1f1f;
    --accent: #c8f542;
    --accent2: #f5a442;
    --accent3: #42c8f5;
    --text: #f0f0f0;
    --muted: #888;
    --border: #2a2a2a;
  }
  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
  body {
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--text);
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    min-height: 100vh;
    padding: 24px 16px 60px;
  }
  .cover-page {
    width: 100%;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-radius: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
  }
  .cover-page img { width: 100%; display: block; border-radius: 20px; }
  .header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 36px;
    padding: 36px 20px 28px;
    background: var(--card);
    border-radius: 20px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .header::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -60px; right: -60px;
    width: 200px; height: 200px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(200,245,66,0.12) 0%, transparent 70%);
    border-radius: 50%;
  }
  .header-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--accent);
    color: #0f0f0f;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 4px 14px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .header h1 {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(42px, 10vw, 72px);
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    line-height: 1;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .header h1 span { color: var(--accent); }
  .header p { color: var(--muted); font-size: 14px; font-weight: 300; }
  .macros {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }
  .macro-card {
    background: var(--card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 16px 12px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .macro-card .val { font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; font-size: 28px; line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .macro-card .label { font-size: 11px; color: var(--muted); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; }
  .macro-card:nth-child(1) .val { color: var(--accent); }
  .macro-card:nth-child(2) .val { color: var(--accent2); }
  .macro-card:nth-child(3) .val { color: var(--accent3); }
  .macro-card:nth-child(4) .val { color: #f542a4; }
  .days-nav {
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    overflow-x: auto;
    padding-bottom: 4px;
    scrollbar-width: none;
  }
  .days-nav::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }
  .day-btn {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    background: var(--card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 8px 16px;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 500;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  .day-btn.active { background: var(--accent); color: #0f0f0f; border-color: var(--accent); font-weight: 600; }
  .day-btn:hover:not(.active) { border-color: var(--accent); color: var(--accent); }
  .day-panel { display: none; }
  .day-panel.active { display: block; }
  .day-title { font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; font-size: 38px; letter-spacing: 2px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: var(--accent); }
  .meal-card {
    background: var(--card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
  }
  .meal-card:hover { border-color: #3a3a3a; }
  .meal-card::before { content: ''; position: absolute; left: 0; top: 0; bottom: 0; width: 3px; border-radius: 3px 0 0 3px; }
  .meal-card.desayuno::before { background: var(--accent2); }
  .meal-card.almuerzo::before { background: var(--accent); }
  .meal-card.cena::before { background: var(--accent3); }
  .meal-card.snack::before { background: #f542a4; }
  .meal-header { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .meal-emoji { font-size: 22px; }
  .meal-type { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--muted); }
  .meal-name { font-size: 17px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text); margin-top: 1px; }
  .meal-kcal { margin-left: auto; font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; font-size: 22px; color: var(--accent); }
  .meal-kcal span { font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 11px; color: var(--muted); font-weight: 400; }
  .ingredients { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 6px; }
  .ingredient { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; padding: 8px 12px; background: var(--card2); border-radius: 8px; font-size: 14px; }
  .ingredient .name { color: var(--text); }
  .ingredient .grams { font-weight: 600; font-size: 13px; color: var(--muted); }
  .meal-macros { display: flex; gap: 8px; margin-top: 12px; }
  .mm { flex: 1; background: var(--card2); border-radius: 8px; padding: 6px 8px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; }
  .mm .mv { font-weight: 600; color: var(--text); }
  .mm .ml { color: var(--muted); font-size: 10px; }
  .snacks-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 10px; margin-top: 4px; }
  .snack-item { background: var(--card2); border-radius: 10px; padding: 12px; font-size: 13px; }
  .snack-item .st { color: var(--muted); font-size: 11px; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .snack-item .sn { color: var(--text); font-weight: 500; }
  .snack-item .sg { color: #f542a4; font-weight: 600; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 2px; }
  .daily-total {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1f0f 0%, #181818 100%);
    border: 1px solid rgba(200,245,66,0.2);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 18px 20px;
    margin-top: 6px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .daily-total .dt-label { font-size: 12px; color: var(--muted); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1.5px; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .daily-total .dt-val { font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; font-size: 32px; color: var(--accent); line-height: 1; }
  .dt-macros { display: flex; gap: 16px; }
  .dt-m { text-align: center; }
  .dt-m .dv { font-weight: 600; color: var(--text); font-size: 15px; }
  .dt-m .dl { font-size: 10px; color: var(--muted); text-transform: uppercase; }
  .tips { margin-top: 28px; background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 16px; padding: 20px; }
  .tips h3 { font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; font-size: 24px; letter-spacing: 2px; color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .tip-item { display: flex; gap: 12px; align-items: flex-start; padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); font-size: 14px; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.5; }
  .tip-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .tip-item .ti { font-size: 18px; flex-shrink: 0; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="cover-page">
  <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/luistrainer6-crypto/sg-gomez/main/portada.png" alt="Plan Alimenticio Personalizado - Sergio Gómez" onerror="this.style.display='none'">
</div>

<div class="header">
  <div class="header-tag">Plan de déficit calórico</div>
  <h1>PLAN <span>NUTRICIONAL</span></h1>
  <p>Sergio Gómez · 31 años · 89.5kg · 1.83m · Entreno mixto 5x semana</p>
</div>

<div class="macros">
